task.summary:
Working on conduits, fluids and other things.
Fixing bugs with non fired Forges. Closes #36

Fixing fluids not checking for Null stacks and tags. Now returns default if a undefined metal is found.
Fixes #37

Updating to a new version of SmithsCore Fixes a bunch of blocks, including a bunch of bugs with the Anvil.
Closes: * SmithsGaming/SmithsCore#12 * SmithsGaming/Armory#38 * SmithsGaming/Armory#42
